Data set: The MOPEX Catalogue

The MOPEX catalogue

data("MOPEXcatalogue")

Format

A data frame with 431 stations (rows) and 12 metadata fields (columns).

stationID

Station id number.

longitude

latitude

elevation

V5

datestart

dateend

V8

V9

state

V11

basin

String describing the river's name.

Source

ftp://hydrology.nws.noaa.gov/pub/gcip/mopex/US_Data/
